title: James Herriot - All Creatures Great and Small  (BBC - Specials)
description:
A collection of the specials which the BBC made with respect to its much loved drama series about the ups and downs of a veterinary practice in the Yorkshire Dales in the first half of the 20th century.



Episodes:

1983 Special - The Lord God Made Them All: 1

1985 Special - The Lord God Made Them All: 2

1990 Special - Brotherly Love

Set Visit (1985)

Stars Reunited (2003).




Enjoy and Seed!!
